---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import ParticleNetwork from '../components/ParticleNetwork.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Free Agile AI Prompt Playbook';
const pageDescription = 'Get 5 copy-paste AI prompts that make you sound technical in sprint planning, refinement, and retrospectives—even if you\'ve never touched ChatGPT before.';
---

<LandingLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <!-- Hero Section with Particle Network Background (matches homepage) -->
  <section class="relative bg-black overflow-hidden min-h-[600px] lg:min-h-[700px] flex items-center">
    <!-- Particle Animation Background -->
    <ParticleNetwork />

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 py-16 lg:py-24 mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 max-w-[1600px] w-full">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left Column - Text Content -->
        <div class="max-w-2xl animate-fade-in">
          <!-- Main Headline (matches homepage h1 styling) -->
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">
            <span class="text-white">How I Got Rehired in </span>
            <span class="text-primary-400">2 Weeks</span>
            <span class="text-white"> After Being Laid Off With Thousands of Other Scrum Masters</span>
          </h1>

          <!-- Subheadline (matches homepage) -->
          <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            When companies started cutting "ceremony-only" agile roles in January 2023, I built automation systems that proved I was technical—not "just a facilitator."
          </p>

          <!-- Value proposition -->
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.25s;">
            This <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">free playbook</span> is your first step to proving technical value.
          </p>

          <!-- CTA Button (matches homepage btn-primary) -->
          <div class="animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
            <a
              href="#get-playbook"
              class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-4 scroll-to-form"
            >
              <span class="relative z-10">Get the Free Playbook</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column - YouTube Video -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in lg:animate-slide-left" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
          <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary-600/20">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="100%"
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9n6UGRKqMjk"
              title="Danny's Agile Automation Story"
              frameborder="0"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              allowfullscreen
              class="w-full h-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Crisis Story Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container section-spacing">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-gray-900 mb-12">
          My Layoff Should Have Been Career-Ending. Instead, I Was Back at Work in 2 Weeks.
        </h2>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
          <p>In January 2023, I was laid off along with thousands of other Scrum Masters.</p>

          <p>My peers spent months searching for interviews. Some are still looking.</p>

          <p>I was back at work within two weeks—landing a Fortune 500 pharmaceutical role.</p>

          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">The difference?</p>

          <p>In every interview, I could prove I built technical systems—not just facilitated meetings.</p>

          <p>I had Jira automation that saved 12 hours per sprint. I had architecture decisions I could defend. I had measurable impact I could demonstrate.</p>

          <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-600">That's not coordination. That's engineering.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Inline Email Form Section -->
  <section id="get-playbook" class="bg-gray-50 scroll-mt-8">
    <div class="section-container section-spacing">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-medium p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-gray-900 text-center mb-4">
          Start Phase 1: Get the FREE Agile AI Prompt Playbook
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-8">
          5 copy-paste AI prompts that make you sound technical in sprint planning, refinement, and retrospectives—even if you've never touched ChatGPT before.
        </p>

        <!-- What's Inside the Playbook -->
        <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">The Story Improver Prompt</strong> — Turn vague requirements into crystal-clear user stories with acceptance criteria in 30 seconds</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">The Acceptance Criteria Builder</strong> — Generate testable, specific acceptance criteria that developers actually understand</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">The Refinement Prep Assistant</strong> — Prepare for refinement in 5 minutes instead of 2 hours—with all edge cases covered</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">The Sprint Summary Generator</strong> — Auto-summarize sprint outcomes for stakeholders without manual report writing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">The Retrospective Theme Analyzer</strong> — Identify patterns from retro notes instantly—spot what's working and what needs attention</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Email Form with ConvertKit -->
        <form action="https://app.convertkit.com/forms/FORM_ID/subscriptions" method="post" data-sv-form="FORM_ID">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email_address"
            placeholder="Enter your email"
            class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-lg border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-500/50 focus:border-primary-500 transition-all duration-200"
            required
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn-primary w-full mt-4 text-lg"
          >
            <span class="relative z-10">Download the Free Playbook</span>
          </button>
        </form>

        <!-- Social Proof -->
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center mt-6">
          Join <strong class="text-gray-900">15,000+ agile professionals</strong> who've downloaded this playbook. Takes 2 minutes to read, saves hours every sprint.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof Statement Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container section-spacing">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-gray-900 mb-12">
          My Automation Systems Never Stop Working. They Don't Take Sick Days. They Just Create Value.
        </h2>

        <div class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="mb-8">While other Scrum Masters were updating Jira tickets manually, my automation systems were:</p>

          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 inline-block text-left">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Syncing sprint dates automatically</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Prepping standup updates before meetings</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Flagging blockers 3 days before they became crises</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Sending stakeholder reports without human intervention</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="mb-4">I quickly realized this wasn't just about efficiency—it was about separating your value from your hours.</p>

          <p class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-10">Companies don't want coordinators anymore. They want architects who build systems.</p>

          <!-- CTA Button -->
          <a
            href="#get-playbook"
            class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-4 scroll-to-form"
          >
            <span class="relative z-10">
              Start with the Free Playbook
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Comes After Section - Teaser -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="section-container section-spacing">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">After the Playbook</p>
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-gray-900 mb-4">
          The Complete Transformation System
        </h2>

        <!-- Intro paragraph -->
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The Prompt Playbook teaches you to <strong class="text-gray-900">sound</strong> technical. The complete system (available after you opt-in) teaches you to <strong class="text-gray-900">BE</strong> technical with:
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Button - Above cards -->
        <a
          href="#get-playbook"
          class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-4 scroll-to-form"
        >
          <span class="relative z-10">
            Start with the Free Playbook
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 Framework Cards (matches homepage card styling) -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
        <!-- Framework 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-gray-900 mb-4">
            The 3-Phase Transformation Path
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The exact career progression from Manual Coordinator → Automation Builder → Agentic Strategist → AI-Powered Architect. Includes time investment for each phase, skills to develop, and career impact at every stage.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-gray-900 mb-4">
            The 5 Automation Patterns That Prove You're Technical
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The Sprint Sync Engine, 12-Minute Standup, Stale Ticket Radar, and automated reporting systems that saved my teams 12+ hours per sprint—and got me hired in 2 weeks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-gray-900 mb-4">
            The Interview Answer Framework
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The exact responses I used when interviewers asked "How do you ensure data accuracy?" and "How do you identify blockers early?" You'll sound technical, not like a meeting facilitator.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-gray-900 mb-4">
            The Self-Assessment Quiz
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Identify where you are right now: Manual Coordinator, Automation Builder, Agentic Strategist, or AI-Powered Architect. Know your starting point to plan your path forward.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-gray-900 mb-4">
            The Career Insurance Checklist
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The 10 technical skills that make you layoff-resistant in 2026. Plus: which skills to prioritize based on your current role (Scrum Master, Product Owner, RTE, Agile Coach).
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-gray-900 mb-4">
            The First 30 Days Roadmap
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Week-by-week action plan to build your first automation system, prove technical value to your team, and start repositioning yourself as an architect (not just a facilitator).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final Closer Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container section-spacing">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-gray-900 mb-12">
          Your Career Is Too Important to Be Limited by Facilitation Skills.
        </h2>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6 mb-10">
          <p>Whether you've been laid off, fear being replaced by AI, or simply want career optionality instead of job dependency—the path is the same.</p>

          <p>Companies aren't cutting agile roles because agile is dead. They're cutting roles that "just coordinate."</p>

          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">The professionals who survive and thrive are the ones who can prove they build systems, architect solutions, and create technical value.</p>

          <p class="text-primary-600 font-bold text-xl">The free playbook is your first step.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Final CTA -->
        <a
          href="#get-playbook"
          class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-4 scroll-to-form"
        >
          <span class="relative z-10">
